<h2>4 key Facebook ads trends to watch in 2024</h2>
<p><span>We know Facebook is one of the best <a href="https://localiq.com/blog/best-advertising-platforms/">advertising platforms available</a>. So before we share some golden advice for creating high-performing <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/facebook-ad-objectives">Facebook ads in 2024</a>, letâ€™s take a look at four Facebook ad trends that will have a big impact on the<a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2022/01/11/most-popular-social-media-platforms" target="_blank" rel="noopener"> social media marketing</a> world.</span></p>
