<h3>2. Leverage the power of UGC across your campaigns</h3>
<p><span>Weâ€™ve already covered the incredible effectiveness of UGC for advertisers, so make sure youâ€™re integrating this content into your Facebook campaigns as often as possible. </span></p>
<p>There are many different types of user-generated content that you can utilize in 2024, from <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/facebook-reviews">product reviews</a> to <a href="https://localiq.com/blog/customer-testimonial-video/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">customer testimonials</a> and organic posts.</p>
<p><span>Since UGC is sourced from real customers, it feels more authentic, trustworthy, and persuasive for potential shoppers. Use this to your advantageâ€”if you can regularly collect and distribute UGC assets on Facebook, then youâ€™ll steadily build brand credibility and generate sales. </span></p>
