<p>To give yourself the biggest number of opportunities to scale, itâ€™s a good idea to start your campaign with a diverse mix of broad audiences. While youâ€™ll always want to allocate a healthy budget for your red-hot retargeting segments, youâ€™ll also need to balance this out with larger audiences that will ensure sufficient scale.</p>
