<p>Itâ€™s all about the <a href="https://searchengineland.com/how-tiktok-algorithm-works-390229" target="_blank" rel="noopener">TikTok algorithm</a>.</p>
<p>Whenever you launch a new TikTok campaign, the algorithm will enter a â€œ<a href="https://ads.tiktok.com/help/article/learning-phase?lang=en">Learning Phase</a>.â€ During this time, the algorithm will expose a range of different audiences to your ads, gathering data on which users are most likely to click and convert. While your CPA may fluctuate in these first few days, it will quickly stabilize once the Learning Phase progresses.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/tiktok-marketing-learning-phase-chart.jpg" alt="tiktok marketing - chart that shows conversions relative to learning phase" width="835" height="398" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-75563" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/tiktok-marketing-learning-phase-chart.jpg 835w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/tiktok-marketing-learning-phase-chart-480x229.jpg 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 835px, 100vw" /></p>
<p>By starting your campaign with a wider audience, you essentially provide the algorithm with the scale it needs to test, optimize, and evolve.</p>
<p>The more users that can be reached throughout the Learning Phase, the faster the algorithm can identify audiences that are converting from your ads, which is crucial for cost efficiency.</p>
<p>While thereâ€™s nothing wrong with focusing on smaller audience segments once youâ€™ve <a href="https://localiq.com/blog/customer-data/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">gathered sufficient data</a>, itâ€™s a good idea to cast a wider net initially. Not only will this help the algorithm to collect performance insights, but it will also help you to dramatically increase conversions in the long run.</p>
<h3>3. Use full-screen vertical videos</h3>
<p>Hereâ€™s a simple <a href="https://upbeatagency.com/tiktok-marketing-strategy/">TikTok strategy</a> that can make a big difference to your conversion rates.</p>
