<p>If prospects click a â€œLearn Moreâ€™â€ CTA, theyâ€™ll want to discover more information about your products. If they click â€œBuy Now,â€ theyâ€™ll probably want to reach the checkout as quickly as possible. Make sure that youâ€™re building a seamless user journey that feels convenient and intuitive, with fast-loading pages and a <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2022/06/15/website-accessibility">clear website structure</a> thatâ€™s easy to navigate.</p>
