<p>TikTok is a social media phenomenon. The platform has swiftly acquired a colossal audience (thatâ€™s still growing) and is now leading the charge when it comes to producing new social trends and <a href="https://localiq.com/blog/types-of-social-media-content/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">social media content ideas</a>.</p>
<p>Influencer-style direct-to-camera videos are hugely popular on TikTok, and this type of content is now infiltrating every social media platform. If you want to avoid falling behind the competition, theyâ€™ll need to embrace the TikTok takeover.</p>
