<p>Advantage+ campaigns have delivered positive returns for many brands so far, so theyâ€™re worth pursuing, particularly for newer advertisers. Plus, Facebook is likely to continue improving the Advantage+ product, meaning these campaigns are a safe bet for the foreseeable future.</p>
